CodeSubmit Plugin
==================

.. contents::

About
-----
This plugin allows the user to submit their codes for programming forums like SPOJ from Geany in C,C++,Python(more languages to be added soon).
At the moment it supports this services:

	* SPOJ

CodeSubmit Plugin detects automatically the current file and submits it to the SPOJ server automatically.


Requirements
------------
	* GTK+ >= 2.12
	* libsoup 2.4 >= 2.4.0
	* Beautiful Soup library for python
	* Poster library for python
	
Installation
------------
This plugin is part of the geany-plugins project.
See the README file of that package.

